      "acceptanceCriteria": "Velocity field predictions agree with PIV measurements within combined experimental and numerical uncertainty bands; hemolysis index predictions within 15% of in-vitro measurements.",
      "rationale": "Area-averaged velocity magnitude error is 4.7% across five operating points; peak velocity discrepancy is 8.1%. Predicted relative hemolysis index deviates from in-vitro measurements by 11.3% at worst case, within the 15% acceptance threshold."
